<title>
Fender Apron Panel, Fender Apron Extension and Suspension Upper Bracket Removal and Installation
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
The figure below shows condition where following parts are removed.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Front fender 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9A06005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Hood lock member, lamp support member and lamp support brace 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B06001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Front fender lower bracket 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B06002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Dash side front panel with cowl top side front panel 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B06006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
