<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06007001">
<title>
General Notes
</title>
<ptxt>
Welding method and number of welding points are the same on both sides. This repair instruction shows procedure for left side.
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06007002">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots and remove fender apron panel, fender apron extension and suspension upper bracket.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70P9B0060.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "233.898mm" ver = "01" gw = "496" gh = "647"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.373in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.373in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Vehicle left side
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[B]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Vehicle right side
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06007003">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Before conducting any weld, check installation position and condition for installation part(s). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B04004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B04009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B04012"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Proceed repair while taking into consideration installation of parts that affect appearance. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B04003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install suspension upper bracket.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct plug weld or resistance spot weld.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0022.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "102.526mm" ver = "02" gw = "327" gh = "274"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install fender apron panel and fender apron extension.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct plug weld or resistance spot weld.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A9B0009.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "212.042mm" ver = "01" gw = "501" gh = "585"/>
